    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/9130f1b24b8d4aa836ee38a3b5ed661f.poster.avif?t=1677800239\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/9130f1b24b8d4aa836ee38a3b5ed661f.webm?t=1677800239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/9130f1b24b8d4aa836ee38a3b5ed661f.mp4?t=1677800239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>被困在一个被怪物蹂躏的被诅咒的岛屿上，你唯一的生存希望是你可信赖的霰弹枪手臂。 穿越险恶的迷你开放世界，在穿过茂密的丛林、浑浊的湖泊、高耸的山脉和破旧的废弃建筑时，穿过成群的僵尸、漂浮的眼睛和爆炸性的恶魔。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/5d634f691eae43cdcd83533044f880e4.poster.avif?t=1677800239\" width=320 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/5d634f691eae43cdcd83533044f880e4.webm?t=1677800239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272770/extras/5d634f691eae43cdcd83533044f880e4.mp4?t=1677800239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你收集必要的零件来修理你的船并逃离时，时钟在滴答作响，怪物正在逼近。你能在这个被诅咒的岛屿的恐怖中幸存下来并活着出来吗？ 现在就来玩，在这个令人心跳加速、充满动作的冒险中找到答案！",
